snippet.textDisplay:
Its surreal!! Speechless, Mind-blowing!!! the only Mohobbat Element I missed was Mohobbat with Almighty!! Ishq - e - Khuda, ALLAH se mohobbat to sab se apex hai, and 2AM is perfect "Tahajjud" time, if they would had created a room where a man or women talking to Almighty, boy the goosebumps there would had been on another level.

Rest its a Masterpiece after Mehram, GO, this made me cry, i can relate to this song, I read somewhere on another video where somebody expressed his thoughts as It is a conversation between a Pessimist and optimist, Pessimist complains the negativity and optimist tells him that Love exists too! if you listen to this song with this perspective the impact goes 100x, and if you observe Star Shah's part showed people all alone and frustrated, while Zeeshans's part is all with couples!! and how can I forget the lyrics every word hits you.

This song will be in my head for sometime now and that sometime is not ending soon!!
